trackName: Anxiety Reliever: Stress and Anxiety Relief
description:
Relax, overcome anxiety and stress and fall asleep faster with the help of Anxiety Reliever. Immerse yourself in a relaxing, supportive and soothing environment.

Anxiety Reliever consists of a Collection of Calming Audio Recordings,  Helpful Guides, Insightful Anxiety Tracker, Breathe and Supportive Messages.

SESSIONS:
Calming audio sessions will help you to overcome anxiety and stress, relax and feel better. All audio sessions are divided into categories: De-Stress, Anxiety, Sleepy Time, Binaural Sounds, ASMR. 

Each session will guide you through stress and anxiety to feeling better and calmer. Please put on your headphones when listening to binaural audio recordings to experience genuine 360° sound

TIPS:
In the Tips section, you will find step-by-step guides covering many topics such as how to overcome anxiety, release painful emotions, how to deal with negative thoughts and so many others. So it’s truly a great tool to fall back on for guidance if you are feeling anxious, sad, stressed, or negative.

TRACKER:
A very important part of overcoming anxiety is identifying your triggers, tracking your habitual thoughts and noticing improvements. It’s a wonderful daily tool that you can use to identify and evaluate your thinking patterns and anxiety triggers.

With this data, you can make a more thoughtful analysis of your mental states and stress levels. 

BREATHE:
Breathe is a guided breathing tool that helps you to calm down in the midst of stress or panic. Just choose your breathing cycle and take deep breaths.

MESSAGES: 
Receive positive and uplifting messages from the AR Team to support you during the hard and challenging times. We believe that kind and loving words have the power to change a person's day! 


PRICING:
Anxiety Reliever is free to download, however, to keep improving and maintaining the app we had to implement an upgrade option for users. 

There are two upgrade options to unlock all the content: 

A Yearly Subscription: $32.99 ($2.75/month) 
A Monthly Subscription: $5.99/month

If you decide to upgrade, you will get unlimited access to sessions, tips, tracker and messages.

These prices are for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence. 

Your annual or monthly subscription will automatically renew at the end of each term, and your credit card will be charged through your iTunes Account. You can turn off auto-renew at any time by going to your iTunes account. However, refunds will not be provided for the unused portion of the time.
